1
00:00:06,125 --> 00:00:08,450
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,537 --> 00:00:11,112
=Episode 3=

3
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:18,320
I'm bleeding.

4
00:00:18,719 --> 00:00:19,600
Why don't I feel pain?

5
00:00:19,920 --> 00:00:20,960
I feel it!

6
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:25,879
How dare you touch my wife!

7
00:00:26,039 --> 00:00:27,559
(Why is he talking to himself?)

8
00:00:27,559 --> 00:00:28,600
(Freak.)

9
00:00:30,199 --> 00:00:31,960
How dare you touch my wife?

10
00:00:40,679 --> 00:00:42,280
Iron skull or something?

11
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:49,341
That actually hurt a bit.

12
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:50,720
(I get it now.)

13
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,200
(In this consciousness space,)

14
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,640
(whoever stands in front)

15
00:00:53,719 --> 00:00:55,280
(takes the physical damage.)

16
00:00:56,437 --> 00:00:57,877
I'll protect you.

17
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:11,200
Zechen, run!

18
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,439
Stop!

19
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:19,400
Why do you always
risk your life to save me?

20
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,439
(Because you're my wife.)

21
00:01:26,359 --> 00:01:28,159
I'm just a fragment
of consciousness right now.

22
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,519
(No matter what you are,)

23
00:01:33,125 --> 00:01:34,965
(I'll always love you.)

24
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:44,719
So hot.

25
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:50,120
You've got a fever.

26
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:57,519
(I've entered his memories.)

27
00:01:58,537 --> 00:01:59,915
(This is his childhood.)

28
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:02,719
Dad! Mom!

29
00:02:03,550 --> 00:02:06,190
Wake up, please!

30
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:13,199
Don't be scared, kids.

31
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,520
Zechen, Zemu,

32
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:17,950
this is me with your parents.

33
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,001
Kids,

34
00:02:23,439 --> 00:02:26,240
your dad was my best friend.

35
00:02:27,319 --> 00:02:30,039
From now on,
I'll take care of you like my own.

36
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,800
Jiang Zechen,

37
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:42,680
you got scolded at school again today.

38
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:45,439
Dad, I'm sorry.

39
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:47,400
I won't do it again.

40
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:49,120
Sorry won't

41
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,159
save you from punishment!

42
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,599
Dad, stop hitting him!

43
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:56,919
He's just a kid!

44
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,280
If you're gonna hit him, hit me too!

45
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,439
Fine.

46
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,960
I'll hit you both

47
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,039
then!

48
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:05,120
You asked for it!

49
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,319
You asked for it!

50
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:10,280
How dare you?

51
00:03:10,919 --> 00:03:13,000
(So this is the kind
of life you've been living?)

52
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:19,599
(Why am I crying?)

53
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:32,879
I

54
00:03:32,879 --> 00:03:35,240
don't know what you're sad about,

55
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,159
but seeing you cry makes me

56
00:03:43,125 --> 00:03:44,324
want to cry too.

57
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:52,520
Come on.

58
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,919
Let's take your body back.

59
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,680
Where did you get a lockpick?

60
00:04:20,812 --> 00:04:21,731
Wen Li gave it to me.

61
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,199
A girl?

62
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,279
Yeah.

63
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:28,800
Don't underestimate her.

64
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,319
She can

65
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:33,040
be tougher than most guys.

66
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,120
Let's check around.

67
00:04:47,079 --> 00:04:48,319
We only have 20 minutes.

68
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:49,879
Go upstairs.

69
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,360
Qiao Nian.

70
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,240
My body!

71
00:05:09,079 --> 00:05:10,639
So it really was Duan Yiran.

72
00:05:20,662 --> 00:05:23,383
Qiao Nian,
time's running out. Let's do it.

73
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,240
Sorry you have
to go through this with me again.

74
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,240
(For you,)

75
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,159
(I'd do anything.)

76
00:05:40,912 --> 00:05:42,725
(This time it'll work.)

77
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,199
Maybe we should get closer.

78
00:06:44,537 --> 00:06:46,300
(Wen Li)

79
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:48,160
Hey,

80
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,839
I've stalled him as much as I can.

81
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:50,800
How's it going on your end?

82
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,040
Qiao Nian!

83
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,879
Wake up! Qiao Nian!

84
00:06:57,199 --> 00:06:58,199
Wake up!

85
00:06:59,775 --> 00:07:03,215
(Zechen, I'm still inside your body.)

86
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,319
It's fine.

87
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,879
I'll take you home first.

88
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,319
We'll figure it out after.

89
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,800
It's you.

90
00:07:26,887 --> 00:07:29,127
What a devoted couple.

91
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:34,199
Take her away.

92
00:07:36,650 --> 00:07:38,530
(Let's see how you handle this.)

93
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:40,600
Ms. Qiao, what should we do with him?

94
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,680
Dump him on the street.

95
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,879
(The next target is the old man.)

96
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:48,759
Mr. Qiao, there's still
no news about Ms. Qiao.

97
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:51,240
The kidnappers haven't made any demands.

98
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,600
What should we do?

99
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,399
Mr. Qiao,

100
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:56,279
the whole company is watching you.

101
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:58,839
With Qiao Nian missing,

102
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,360
the group is unstable.

103
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:02,959
Internal conflict is getting worse.

104
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:06,399
We can't go without leadership.

105
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,319
If I may,

106
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:14,920
Wenjun is the best choice for CEO.

107
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,160
Everyone trusts her.

108
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,519
Until Qiao Nian returns,

109
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:24,120
I'm still chairman.

110
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:26,000
(Old man,)

111
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:28,120
(you're pushing me too far.)

112
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:32,120
Everyone, go back to work.

113
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,120
Okay.

114
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,759
(Since bribery didn't work,)

115
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:39,919
(don't blame me for being ruthless.)

116
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,639
Zhou,

117
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,840
find Qiao Nian.

118
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,480
No matter the cost.

119
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:48,039
Yes, Mr. Qiao.

120
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:54,879
(The kidnappers are definitely
someone inside the company.)

121
00:08:55,287 --> 00:08:56,750
(Qiao Group)

122
00:08:56,799 --> 00:08:59,000
Mr. Bai,

123
00:08:59,399 --> 00:09:00,240
you're dismissed.

124
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,840
Ms. Qiao, what about Yiran and me?

125
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,840
Get out!

126
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:13,480
Mom,

127
00:09:14,159 --> 00:09:16,440
I was going to surprise you,

128
00:09:16,759 --> 00:09:18,799
but something went wrong.

129
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:20,639
A surprise?

130
00:09:21,787 --> 00:09:23,667
This?

131
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:29,480
Mom, it was you!

132
00:09:29,519 --> 00:09:30,840
I thought it was Zechen.

133
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,639
Where's Qiao Nian now?

134
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,360
Useless!

135
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:37,120
Why did I even have you?

136
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:40,639
Mom, don't be angry.

137
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:42,759
You really are naive.

138
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:45,799
Jiang Zechen is already at your door.

139
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,879
How am I supposed
to make Qiao Nian disappear now?

140
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:50,080
Look at this mess you've made!

141
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,039
You've ruined everything!

142
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:55,279
Don't worry, Mom.

143
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,639
I'll fix it.

144
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,159
I won't leave any trace.

145
00:09:58,279 --> 00:10:01,799
Trace? You and Bai Niansheng are already

146
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:03,000
my biggest problem.

147
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,799
Should I get rid of you too?

148
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,360
Mom,

149
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,039
I just wanted to help you take

150
00:10:11,412 --> 00:10:13,159
the company and shares first.

151
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:14,240
Shares?

152
00:10:14,937 --> 00:10:17,639
If Jiang Xiao finds out,

153
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,399
everything will be lost.

154
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,639
Mom,

155
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:25,039
I just wanted to prove I'm not

156
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:27,320
worse than Qiao Nian!

157
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:29,200
Mom,

158
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,919
I just want a little more

159
00:10:32,399 --> 00:10:33,759
of your attention and care.

160
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:37,279
I know exactly what you're capable of.

161
00:10:38,159 --> 00:10:38,639
If I hadn't

162
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:41,080
been cleaning up
your mess all these years,

163
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,240
do you really think
your dealings with Bai Niansheng

164
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,480
would've stayed hidden
from your grandpa?

165
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:47,559
Do you want him to hate you even more?

166
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:48,720
Mom,

167
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,120
I was wrong.

168
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:51,840
I really was.

169
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:52,799
I know I messed up.

170
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,000
Bai Niansheng

171
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,279
led me into it.

172
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:58,240
Mom, you can fix this, right?

173
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:01,159
You always have a way.

174
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:03,360
Come here.

175
00:11:08,759 --> 00:11:09,919
At this point,

176
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,399
there's only one option left.

177
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:26,480
(Good thing I kept a backup plan.)

178
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:32,000
Why is this guy here?

179
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,000
(Life countdown: 4 days)
He's awake.

180
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,360
What happened to him?

181
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:36,910
(Where am I?)

182
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:40,759
I'm hungry.

183
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:42,679
Let's eat first.

184
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:46,559
(Whatever his reasons are,)

185
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:48,000
(he can't betray Grandpa.)

186
00:11:48,279 --> 00:11:49,360
(I'll mess with him a bit.)

187
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,919
Hey handsome,
what would you like to eat?

188
00:11:53,159 --> 00:11:55,200
One bowl of noodles.
No cilantro, no spice.

189
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,360
Hey.

190
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,519
Wait.

191
00:11:58,799 --> 00:12:00,759
Extra cilantro, extra spicy.

192
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:01,639
Extra cilantro,

193
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:02,600
extra spicy.

194
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,600
Got it.

195
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,960
You know I can't eat spicy food.

196
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,559
You hid so much from me

197
00:12:14,759 --> 00:12:16,159
and even hurt Grandpa.

198
00:12:16,787 --> 00:12:19,468
You deserve this.

199
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,000
Here's your noodles.

200
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:30,159
That was fast.

201
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:33,080
We're all about speed and hygiene here.

202
00:12:33,725 --> 00:12:34,524
Hmm.

203
00:12:35,612 --> 00:12:37,737
No.

204
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,641
Try it.

205
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,879
(No, I can't.)

206
00:12:44,879 --> 00:12:45,762
(I can't eat that.)

207
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:51,759
Still laughing?

208
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,480
Hey,

209
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,320
what's the situation?

210
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,200
I'm coming to pick you up.

211
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,759
I'll send you the location.

212
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:06,840
No need. I've got
the noodle shop locked in on my GPS.

213
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:07,960
I'm at the door.

214
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:11,399
(Wen Li)
I'm in. Where are you?

215
00:13:12,279 --> 00:13:13,440
I don't see you.

216
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,240
Turn around.

217
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,840
The car that dumped you
on the road is parked here.

218
00:13:24,012 --> 00:13:25,240
(Why is it at the hospital?)

219
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,120
(Qiao Nian must be here too.)

220
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,559
Wait here.

221
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:31,879
Hey, wait.

222
00:13:33,519 --> 00:13:34,360
What's this?

223
00:13:34,475 --> 00:13:36,715
Secret infiltration gear.

224
00:13:39,399 --> 00:13:40,519
I've got a few more gadgets.

225
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:42,559
They'll get you through anywhere.

226
00:13:43,639 --> 00:13:46,679
These glasses and gloves
are my latest inventions.

227
00:13:47,039 --> 00:13:48,440
They let us communicate in real time,

228
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,879
predict the opponent's moves,

229
00:13:50,159 --> 00:13:52,039
and even auto-counterattack.

230
00:13:53,039 --> 00:13:53,840
Hmm.

231
00:13:55,559 --> 00:13:58,480
You're not using me
as a test subject again, are you?

232
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:01,759
No experiments. Just combat.

233
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,559
Good luck.

234
00:14:11,799 --> 00:14:12,399
Oh, you came?

235
00:14:12,399 --> 00:14:14,879
Yeah.

236
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,080
See, I was right, wasn't I?

237
00:14:17,679 --> 00:14:19,039
You can sync with my vision?

238
00:14:19,279 --> 00:14:20,919
Of course. Don't worry,

239
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,840
I'll clear the path.

240
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,960
Show them who's in charge.

241
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,399
Alright.

242
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,519
I'll try.

243
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,960
(This guy is so weird.)

244
00:14:47,919 --> 00:14:48,679
What's wrong?

245
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,039
Nothing.

246
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,879
Just a sudden feeling.

247
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:55,887
I'm fine now.

248
00:14:58,962 --> 00:15:01,122
My body should be in that room.

249
00:15:06,399 --> 00:15:07,600
Do you even know how to drive?

250
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:08,559
Look at this damage!

251
00:15:08,559 --> 00:15:09,799
Sorry, sir.

252
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:11,879
I'll pay for it.

253
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,879
Uh oh,

254
00:15:19,879 --> 00:15:20,720
it's a trap.

255
00:15:27,919 --> 00:15:29,279
(So they were waiting for me?)

256
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,639
(Fine, let's get it done.)

257
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:41,480
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

258
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:49,360
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

259
00:15:49,410 --> 00:15:53,200
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

260
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:57,000
♪Where this ends♪

261
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:04,280
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

262
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:08,610
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

263
00:16:08,650 --> 00:16:11,730
♪Love turns into pain♪

264
00:16:11,800 --> 00:16:15,920
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

265
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:19,560
♪Yet I still want you close♪

266
00:16:19,560 --> 00:16:23,730
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

267
00:16:23,730 --> 00:16:27,040
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

268
00:16:27,040 --> 00:16:31,610
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

269
00:16:31,610 --> 00:16:37,920
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

270
00:16:38,510 --> 00:16:42,700
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

271
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:45,920
♪Love turns into pain♪

272
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:50,360
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

273
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:53,710
♪Yet I still want you close♪

274
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:57,940
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

275
00:16:57,980 --> 00:17:01,200
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

276
00:17:01,330 --> 00:17:05,920
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

277
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:13,000
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪
